paper_title: Some links between $F$-harmonicity, submersion and cohomology
abstract: By studying cohomology classes that are related with $p$-harmonic morphisms, $F$-harmonic maps, and $f$-harmonic maps, we extend several of our previous results on Riemannian submersions and $p$-harmonic morphisms to $F$-harmonic maps, and $f$-harmonic maps which are submersions.
publication_venue: 12 pages. arXiv admin note: substantial text overlap with arXiv:2302.14019
